## Image Generation

Images were generated using Cloudflare Workers AI (FLUX-1-schnell model).

## Audio Generation

Audio files were generated using Edge TTS (Text-to-Speech).

## Story Attribution

This is a simplified, child-friendly adaptation of the classic Chinese novel
"Water Margin" (水浒传) by Shi Nai'an, intended for educational purposes.